WEBVTT

00:00:00.759 --> 00:00:04.700
I have a confession to make,
right off the bat.

00:00:04.724 --> 00:00:07.349
I don't know what you were doing at 16,

00:00:07.373 --> 00:00:10.272
but I'm a really big fan of "Harry Potter"

00:00:10.296 --> 00:00:13.570
and was waiting way too long
to receive my letter

00:00:13.594 --> 00:00:17.023
inviting me to Hogwarts School
of Witchcraft and Wizardry --

00:00:17.047 --> 00:00:18.694
I could have gone for sixth form.

00:00:19.143 --> 00:00:24.509
I was also waiting
for an invitation to the Jedi Temple

00:00:24.533 --> 00:00:28.935
or a tap on the shoulder
to invite me to the X-Men.

00:00:29.464 --> 00:00:30.711
I was that kid.